{"tid":82644,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"蚎, 蝗劣食侵入, 請大家堅持廣東傳統美食","createTime":"2017-01-16T06:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T01:43:33.000Z","uid":75299,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2e69e44142072cbc7de2dd13ab4484d86602a71","tid":82644,"uid":75299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:19:55.000Z","msg":"蚎式劣食(劣食文化代表) - 牛肉飯, 放題, 燒肉, 大阪燒, 鱆魚燒, 炸豬扒<br />\n<br />\n蝗式劣食(劣食文化代表) - 麻辣, 水煮, 雞煲, 烤魚, 小蟲蝦<br />\n<br />\n大家請補充<br />\n<br />\n蚎式劣食多數係明治時期, 戰後貧窮夾硬整出來<br />\n<br />\n蝗式劣食係因為內陸魚肉皆臭, 夾硬遮左浸味<br />\n<br />\n請大家堅持廣東傳統美食, 不要浪費南粵美食傳統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462a45b1d0e9aec8ca61b9b9ae2009438e2e1ae2","tid":82644,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3da63c7a0c765516424e97617f24b752363fbfc","tid":82644,"uid":3500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:25:29.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"86b54059c668dd7ff7630ff84d3af5c2bab26c22","tid":82644,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:27:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蝗式劣食(劣食文化代表) - 麻辣, 水煮, 雞煲, 烤魚, 小蟲蝦<br />\n<br />\n大家請補充<br />\n<br />\n蝗式劣食係因為內陸魚肉皆臭, 夾硬遮左浸味<br />\n<br />\n請大家堅持廣東傳統美食, 不要浪費南粵美食傳統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論"},{"pid":"28c1f54312d8f6fac9dfe96f7997824aefcc9c82","tid":82644,"uid":15,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a834516654abb9ac12a6e941b15f0e